deployLendingPool().details: This function creates a new LendingPool instance with the provided parameters. Only the factory contract should call this function to ensure proper pool management. Requirements: - Caller must be the factory contract

deployLendingPool().notice: Deploys a new LendingPool contract with specified parameters
